Simple Invoices
This is the about pages
Simple Invoices focuses on the basic needs on invoicing yet attempts to allow advanced user more flexibility without compromising simplicity
Our work on Simple Invoices is driven by the philosophy to create the best invoicing software available by using free and open source software and have alot of fun on the way!!
The best way to get involved in the Simple Invoices project is to download and install Simple Invoices and post your ideas, queries, bugs, documentation, request for help, whatever, in our forums all ideas etc are welcome, the more the better !
